<a name="toc_tc30874"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P236-66: TC01_ValidData_IntegrationSuccess&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">rednicluca</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verifică integrarea de succes &icirc;ntre Service și Validatorul real. Testul confirmă că un obiect Stoc cu date corecte trece de validare și ajunge să apeleze metoda de salvare din Repository-ul (Mock).</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><ul>
	<li>
	<p>Obiect Stoc valid:&nbsp;ID: 1, Nume: &quot;Lapte&quot;, Cantitate: 20.0, StocMinim: 5.0.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>Validatorul real este utilizat pentru a procesa regulile de business.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p><strong>Mapare Java (Custom Field):</strong>&nbsp;testAddStoc_ValidData_IntegrationSuccess</p>
	</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.StocServiceIntegrationTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >testAddStoc_ValidData_IntegrationSuccess</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">rsir3617_F01:  Adaugare Produs [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc30876"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P236-67: TC02_InvalidData_QuantityBelowMin&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">rednicluca</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verifică dacă integrarea oprește corect salvarea c&acirc;nd datele sunt invalide. Testul confirmă că Validatorul real aruncă o&nbsp;ValidationException&nbsp;c&acirc;nd cantitatea este sub pragul minim, iar Repository-ul nu este apelat.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><ul>
	<li>
	<p>Obiect Stoc invalid:&nbsp;Cantitate: 2.0, StocMinim: 10.0.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>Se verifică faptul că metoda&nbsp;save()&nbsp;din Repo nu este executată niciodată &icirc;n acest scenariu.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p><strong>Mapare Java (Custom Field):</strong>&nbsp;testAddStoc_InvalidData_IntegrationFails</p>
	</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.StocServiceIntegrationTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >testAddStoc_InvalidData_IntegrationFails</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">rsir3617_F02:  Gestionarea stocului de ingrediente [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc30878"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P236-68: TC03_InvalidData_BoundaryCondition&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">rednicluca</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Test de integrare pentru condiții la limită. Se verifică dacă sistemul acceptă un produs unde cantitatea este exact egală cu stocul minim (valoare critică &icirc;n logica de business).</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><ul>
	<li>
	<p>Obiect Stoc la limită:&nbsp;Cantitate: 5.0, StocMinim: 5.0.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>Se confirmă că validatorul real permite trecerea datelor către stratul de persistență.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p><strong>Mapare Java (Custom Field):</strong>&nbsp;testAddStoc_ValidData_Boundary_IntegrationSuccess</p>
	</li>
</ul>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.StocServiceIntegrationTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >testAddStoc_InvalidName_IntegrationFails</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">rsir3617_F02:  Gestionarea stocului de ingrediente [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
